## 7. Authentication Middleware

كل route محتاج auth لازم يكون عنده `authenticate` middleware.

```ts
// ✅ CORRECT
router.get('/',     authenticate, GoalsController.list);
router.post('/',    authenticate, GoalsController.create);
router.put('/:id',  authenticate, GoalsController.update);
router.delete('/:id', authenticate, GoalsController.delete);

// ✅ Public routes — explicitly mark them
router.post('/login',    AuthController.login);    // public intentionally
router.post('/register', AuthController.register); // public intentionally

// ❌ WRONG — route محمية بدون middleware
router.post('/upgrade',   BillingController.upgrade);  // ❌ missing authenticate
router.get('/profile',    ProfileController.get);       // ❌ missing authenticate
router.delete('/:id',     GoalsController.delete);      // ❌ missing authenticate
```

