## 12. Database Rules

### كل model لازم عنده index على userId

```prisma
// ✅ CORRECT
model Goal {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId    String
  title     String
  status    String   @default("active")
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([userId, status])
  @@index([userId, createdAt])
}

// ❌ WRONG — full table scan على كل request
model Goal {
  id     String @id
  userId String
  // missing @@index([userId])
}
```

### ممنوع N+1 — استخدم bulk queries

```ts
// ✅ CORRECT
const tickers = holdings.map(h => h.ticker);
const prices = await getBulkPrices(tickers); // request واحد

// ❌ WRONG
for (const holding of holdings) {
  holding.price = await getPrice(holding.ticker); // N requests
}
```

### استخدم Redis للـ expensive queries

```ts
// ✅ CORRECT
const cacheKey = `prices:${ticker}`;
const cached = await getCache(cacheKey);
if (cached) return cached;

const fresh = await fetchFromYahoo(ticker);
await setCache(cacheKey, fresh, CACHE_TTL.prices);
return fresh;

// ❌ WRONG — hit database/API على كل request
return fetchFromYahoo(ticker);
```

